sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nguoi dung
    participant FE as Chat UI
    participant API as Chat API
    participant Detector as Quality Detector
    participant DB as Conversation DB
    participant Queue as Review Queue
    participant Admin as NLP Admin

    U->>FE: Hoi cau hoi
    FE->>API: Gui message
    API->>Detector: Danh gia confidence, fallback, sentiment, repeat
    alt Xu ly khong tot
        Detector-->>API: Mark unresolved/low_quality
        API->>DB: Luu conversation + label
        API->>Queue: Tao item can review
        Queue-->>Admin: Xuat hien trong danh sach can gan nhan
    else Xu ly tot
        Detector-->>API: OK
        API->>DB: Luu binh thuong
    end
    API-->>FE: Tra cau tra loi hoac fallback
